# LAB: Relevance Scoring & Rerankers for Trustworthy AI — EU AI Act

Advanced RAG system demonstrating how reranking improves retrieval quality on legal and ethics documents.

## Project Structure

```
├── data/
│   ├── eu_ai_act.pdf
│   ├── ai_hleg_ethics_guidelines_for_trustworthy_ai-en_(...).pdf
│   ├── ethics_guidelines_for_trustworthy_ai-fr_(...).pdf   ← skipped (FR)
│   ├── The_Blueprint_For_Trustworthy_AI.m4a
│   └── The_Blueprint_For_Trustworthy_AI_transcript.txt     ← auto-generated
├── relevance_scoring_rerankers.ipynb
├── lab_summary.md
├── .env                  ← NOT committed (API keys)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md
```

## How to Run

### 1. Prerequisites
- Python 3.12+
- Anaconda environment (`myenv`)
- ffmpeg installed: `brew install ffmpeg`
- OpenAI API key (with billing enabled)
- Pinecone API key (free tier sufficient)

### 2. Install Dependencies
Run Cell 0 in the notebook (once), or:
```bash
pip install langchain==1.2.17 langchain-openai==1.2.1 langchain-community==0.4.1 \
    langchain-pinecone==0.2.13 pinecone openai pypdf python-dotenv \
    tiktoken pandas tqdm pydub
```

### 3. Configure `.env`
```
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...
PINECONE_API_KEY=...
```

### 4. Run Notebook
Open `relevance_scoring_rerankers.ipynb` and run cells sequentially:

| Cell | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| 0 | Install dependencies (run once, then comment out) |
| 1 | Load API keys from `.env` |
| 2 | Create Pinecone index (`trustworthy-ai-lab`, 1536-dim, cosine) |
| 3 | Load PDFs with metadata tagging |
| 4 | Transcribe podcast audio via Whisper (cached after first run) |
| 5 | Chunk all documents (800 chars, 150 overlap) |
| 6 | Generate embeddings → upload to Pinecone |
| 7 | Baseline retrieval (k=5, no reranking) |
| 8 | Baseline with similarity scores |

## Data Sources

| File | Type | Chunks | Category |
|------|------|--------|----------|
| `eu_ai_act.pdf` | PDF | 1030 | `eu_ai_act` |
| `ai_hleg_ethics_guidelines_...-en.pdf` | PDF | 257 | `ethics_guidelines` |
| `The_Blueprint_For_Trustworthy_AI.m4a` | Audio → Whisper | 25 | `trustworthy_ai_podcast` |

**Total: 1,312 chunks** — `text-embedding-3-small` (1536 dimensions) — Pinecone Serverless

## Key Technical Decisions

| Choice | Rationale |
|--------|-----------|
| `text-embedding-3-small` | Cost-efficient, strong semantic performance |
| Pinecone Serverless | Persistent, no infra management |
| `chunk_size=800` | Balances context richness vs. precision for legal text |
| Whisper chunking | Splits audio into 10-min segments to bypass 25MB API limit |
| FR document excluded | Prevents language mixing in retrieval |

